7. Data Requirements (API Needs)
7.1 Insight Feed
Required fields:
insight_id
current_version
opportunity_statement
confidence_score
risk_band
status
relevance_window_end
updated_at
7.2 Insight Detail
Required fields:
Insight record (versioned)
Evidence bundle items
Scoring results + breakdown
Risk profile
Narrative
Decay model
Governance linkage
7.3 Version History
Required fields:
List of versions
Delta metadata
Transition history
8. Non-Functional Requirements
Fast read performance (ranked list must be instant)
Traceability (every displayed claim links to evidence)
Audit friendliness (stable IDs, version pins)
No execution affordances (no “run” buttons)
